Title: Whirlpool — The Heart of Home
Author: wavelet-director

INT. SUNLIT KITCHEN - MORNING

A cream-white tilt-head stand mixer sits centered on a thick marble counter. Golden morning light rakes in from a window camera-left. Dust motes drift in the air. The mixer head lifts open with slow ceremony, revealing a polished stainless bowl beneath.

CUT TO:

INT. SUNLIT KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS

Extreme close. The spiral dough hook turns inside the bowl, folding pale enriched dough into a glossy mass. Streaks of melting butter catch the window light. The motion is slow and deliberate.

CUT TO:

INT. SUNLIT KITCHEN - CONTINUOUS

The camera pulls back. The mixer rests beside a linen-draped boule of risen dough on a wooden board. A coffee cup steams at the edge of frame. The kitchen breathes.

FADE OUT.
